Role is determined from **Asian Handicap**.

Authoritative rule:
- any team giving the negative handicap is the favourite
- do not mirror the rule by venue

## 7.1 Pick-em
`|AH| ≤ 0.25`

## 7.2 DNB equivalence
`AH = DNB ≡ 0`

So DNB is treated the same as AH 0.

## 7.3 Narrow Favourite
`AH = -0.5`

## 7.4 Moderate Favourite
`AH = -0.75 to -1.25`

## 7.5 Strong Favourite
`AH ≤ -1.5`

## 7.6 Underdog
Any non-favourite team in a non-pick-em match.
